24 in the daily course of the clerk's business or as may be ordered by a court; and
25 (3) Not be subject to the provisions of KRS Chapter 41 relating to the deposit of money
26 in the State Treasury until by action of a court, such as forfeiture of a bond, the
27 money is due and owing to the Commonwealth.
